1. *Vere* se da će sutra biti lepo vreme. (It is believed that tomorrow will be nice weather.)
2. Da li *vereš* u to što ti pričam? (Do you believe what I'm telling you?)
3. Oni *veruju* da će njihov tim pobediti. (They believe their team will win.)
4. Njegova *vera* je veoma važna za njega. (His faith is very important to him.)
5. *Verujem* da ćeš uspeti ako se potrudiš. (I believe you will succeed if you try.)
6. Bez *vere* u sebe, ne možeš postići ništa. (Without belief in yourself, you cannot achieve anything.)
7. *Verovala* je da će se stvari popraviti, ali nije bila u pravu. (She believed things would improve, but she was wrong.)
8. Njihova *vera* je drugačija od moje, ali ih poštujem. (Their faith is different from mine, but I respect them.)
9. *Verovatno* ćeš morati da čekaš još neko vreme. (You will probably have to wait a little longer.)
10. Molim te, *veruj* mi, nisam to uradio. (Please believe me, I didn't do it.)